# Move the Y-endstop and remove the drag chains

The X-endstop fit nicely on the toolhead but the LDO Trident kit I bought came with an XY-endstop PCB mounted on the XY rail.
It works well but it requires a drag chain to the XY-carriage.

# What's next?

I've really been wanting multi color support and I've been waiting for [ERCF][] to be ready for ages.
But I'll probably skip [ERCF][] in favor of the [Box Turtle][] instead as it seems easier to get working.

